==English==
===Etymology===
[[love]] + [[feast]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# a symbolic meal eaten to celebrate [[brotherly love]], particularly one practiced by early [[Christian]]s celebrating [[agape]].
# a banquet or gathering to promote [[goodwill]] among the participants.

